  "detailed_description": "<strong>~MAJONEKO~</strong><br>The evil Queen from the Highlands has kidnapped our prince.<br>Is your duty to save him!<br>Become Hikare a witch cat with a magic ball that teleports you whenever it touches the floor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445490/extras/9bdf4e15828bb4df856628b9a56f55a2.avif?t=1687107379\" width=567 height=319 /></span><br><br><strong>~A Hard Puzzle Platformer~</strong><br>Predict trajectories and risk falling to the bottom, Majoneko is a platformer but you cant jump.<br>You will fall over and over again...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445490/extras/fd4efedcc273296ddd593c056416c4c3.avif?t=1687107379\" width=566 height=318 /></span><br><br><strong>~Climb to the top!~</strong><br>Go fast or the prince wont be avitable anymore!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445490/extras/45c2e288d4438243069748bb68568c33.avif?t=1687107379\" width=567 height=319 /></span><br><br><strong>~LeaderBoards~</strong><br>Try to beat your times and get into the top 10 in the Hall Of Fame.",
